Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.98,0:03:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Select
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,惡已經決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.16,0:03:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都準備好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.99,0:03:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.84,0:03:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,現在開始排除惡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,機械熊能量開始充填
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.73,0:03:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,嗶哩嗶哩 下作下～作
