Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是真心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,只要在法庭上得到他們的百合承認
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,熊就能變成女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.09,0:07:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,但是要想得到百合承認就必須捨棄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,自己最珍貴的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.76,0:07:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.49,0:07:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然這只是露露的猜測
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.74,0:08:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,但是那時的銀子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是把從紅紅那裡得到的愛意捨棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.92,0:08:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,露露
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.24,0:08:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你說錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.73,0:08:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,為了實現願望而捨棄愛意的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不是銀子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.44,0:08:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,而是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.40,0:08:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,百合裁判就此開庭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.12,0:08:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,被告人 椿輝紅羽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.24,0:08:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你有要申述的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.91,0:08:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我想永遠和銀子在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.71,0:08:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,所以求求你們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.98,0:08:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,請將銀子變成人類的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.60,0:08:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,裁判長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,被告犯下了傲慢之罪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,有罪 Guilty
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,傲慢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,傲慢就是想要改變百合城銀子身份的想法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,這是沒辦法的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.66,0:08:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,因為熊是會被排除的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,而且銀子她成為人之後一定會更幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.20,0:09:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,嗚哇 真有自信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.62,0:09:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,鋥鋥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.42,0:09:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才說你的想法是傲慢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.18,0:09:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是傲慢也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.85,0:09:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.84,0:09:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,請將銀子變成人類的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.69,0:09:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.91,0:09:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不過有一個條件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.11,0:09:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你必須捨棄愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,簡而言之 你會忘記銀子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.14,0:09:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,夢醒時分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.82,0:09:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你就會拒絕她了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,拒絕？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.69,0:09:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.86,0:09:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我許下了不能許下的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.79,0:09:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,誤以為自己那一廂情願的愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,便是世間真理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.01,0:09:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,等待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.52,0:09:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那一刻終會到來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.98,0:09:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,透明風暴呼嘯而至之時
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你將會找到百合城銀子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.27,0:10:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,倘若你和她再次成為朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.90,0:10:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,成功交換誓約之吻的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你們就能永遠在一起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,鋥鋥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.03,0:10:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼被告人 椿輝紅羽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,請回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你要讓百合城銀子成為人類嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.01,0:10:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,抑或 你要放棄愛意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會放棄愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,請將銀子變成人類的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.85,0:10:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,露露
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.30,0:10:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我以最珍貴的東西為代價
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.87,0:10:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,許下了想讓銀子成為人類的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.55,0:10:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,百合裁判就此開庭
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================B-PART====================
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,被告人 椿輝紅羽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.48,0:11:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你承認自己的罪行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.08,0:11:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我承認
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾經犯下了傲慢之罪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.35,0:11:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,許下了想讓銀子成為人類女孩子的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.52,0:11:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 在透明風暴之中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.20,0:11:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你找到自己的所求了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.30,0:11:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,有一個女孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:25.87,Text1,,0,0,100,,{\fad(450,0)}回 憶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.40,0:11:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,教給了我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.37,0:11:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.58,0:11:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,把我的所求——真心愛意找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,純花
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.62,0:11:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我不再害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,只要不忘記愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.05,0:12:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,就永遠不會孤單
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.18,0:12:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,只要不放棄愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.21,0:12:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,即使有所失去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.84,0:12:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,也不會變得透明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我願縱身墜入風暴之中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.10,0:12:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,這… 這算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.04,0:12:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,露露 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.82,0:12:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我會把這顆星星…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.51,0:12:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,把真正的愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.06,0:12:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,交給銀子的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.42,0:12:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.05,0:12:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,下作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.80,0:12:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.45,0:12:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.39,0:13:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你才不是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.60,0:13:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,嗷嗚嗷嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我是食人熊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.54,0:13:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,獨孤求愛的銀子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.42,0:13:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我是來吃你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.19,0:13:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.54,0:13:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,快點開槍打死我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.42,0:13:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不然的話我就要把大家全吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我是罪熊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.60,0:13:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嗷嗚嗷嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,銀子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.01,0:13:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.79,0:13:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,紅羽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.92,0:13:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,終於 找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.48,0:13:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我有一個願望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.14,0:13:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,熊利亞大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.99,0:13:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 熊利亞大人她…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.57,0:14:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,要恢復原貌了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 我們也該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.16,0:14:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,這才是Sexy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.76,0:14:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,嚇啵嗒～嘟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,真是Cool
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,鋥鋥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.53,0:14:55.58,Text1,,25,0,135,,{\fad(350,0)}熊利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.53,0:14:55.58,Text2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,0)}{\pos(746,673)\fsp0\fscx110}愛之星
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.23,0:14:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,椿輝紅羽
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.30,0:14:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你的愛意 是真心？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:14:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是真心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.61,0:15:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,…打碎我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,熊利亞大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.63,0:15:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,請您將我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.14,0:15:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,變成熊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.26,0:15:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,百合 承認
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.74,0:16:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,這… 這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.87,0:16:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,紅羽…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.02,0:16:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,這到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.38,0:16:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,銀子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.06,0:16:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你始終不忘記愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.34,0:16:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你始終不放棄愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.02,0:16:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我給你… 誓約之吻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:16:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我們從今以後永遠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.38,0:17:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,永遠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.31,0:17:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,嗷嗚嗷嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,百合 承認
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.34,0:17:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,超… 超不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,人竟然變成了熊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.07,0:17:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,多麼可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.32,0:17:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,下作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.94,0:18:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我們 已經不忍心開炮了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.41,0:18:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,下作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.76,0:18:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你… 你們在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那已經不是人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.21,0:18:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是熊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.56,0:18:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.30,0:18:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,惡必須排除
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.31,0:18:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,別猶豫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.08,0:18:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,別思考
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.66,0:18:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,開槍！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.89,0:19:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,在我們的齊心協力之下終於做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.76,0:19:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我們成功地排除了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.04,0:19:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,蔓延在這所學園裡的可怕的惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.29,0:19:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,到頭來我們還是不得不成為透明的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.71,0:19:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,現在 讓我們開始排除儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.19,0:19:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友 是重於一切的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.06,0:19:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,此刻在這裡的朋友 就是我們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:51.25,Text1,,0,0,100,,回 憶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.00,0:19:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,開槍！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,無法融入我們的人是在給我們添麻煩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.71,0:20:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,這種不合群的人就是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.44,0:20:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.80,0:20:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,現在 讓我們決定下一個需要排除的惡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,下…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.56,0:20:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,下…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.63,0:21:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,下作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.66,0:21:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,下作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.72,0:21:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,下作？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.82,0:21:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,下作？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.55,0:21:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,找到你了
